          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;"><strong>🇷🇺 Russia:</strong>    
          The Kremlin dismissed the Turkish and Arab media <a href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-25-dec-2024-8-report" target="_blank">report</a> that Asma al-Assad, wife of former Syrian President Bashar al-Assad, filed for divorce and sought to return to the UK. They called these claims false, alongside reports of Assad's confinement in Moscow. The Assad family fled Syria after his regime's overthrow, with Asma facing legal and political scrutiny in the UK. Also, while Asma is a subject of the UK, her nationality has the potential to be revoked, and she could face a lifetime ban in the UK.</p>
